title: Missing the Purple pumpkin icon
body: During the Teemoing event I gifted a friend a mystery skin chest in thinking that it would give me the icon and I have not recieved it yet. Today when I logged on I saw that I have received the Devil Teemo one and figured that the pumpkin one would also be right after it but it was not. So I was wondering if those were still being sent out or if the mystery chests dont count as gifts towards earning that icon. Was just curious. Thank you in advance.

replies.body: Icons are stilling rolling out, with an aim to finish by the 17th per the [Teemoing ](http://na.leagueoflegends.com/en/featured/skins/the-teemoing-2016)page.  Hang tight until then, and the godies will come!
All goood I guess I just assumed they would come together because they are from the same event but we all know what happens when we assume lol
